Screen Size:
  Desktop=992px
  Tablet=768px-991px
  Phone=767px
1 page only
1 page heading
3 sections in a row
Layout:
  Desktop=all 3 sections should use up equal screen space even while making browser window small and big and use float
  Tablet=first 2 rows should be equal and third should be in next line and take up full line
  Mobile:each row shoul take up a single row
Each section should have a section title in top left corner in every device
Dummy text should be pushed down and not collide with the section heading
Set a black border on both the section and section title region that is 1px thick
Set the font size of the heading and section title to be 75% larger and 25% larger (respectively) than the font size of the dummy text
Type lorem and then press tab to get dummy text
